body_html:
An incremental build on a 2013 MBP with just touching one file and running

time ./tensorflow/contrib/makefile/build_all_ios.sh -T -a arm64

gives:

real    0m8.845s
user    0m6.934s
sys     0m1.638s

body:
An incremental build on a 2013 MBP with just touching one file and running
    
    time ./tensorflow/contrib/makefile/build_all_ios.sh -T -a arm64
    
gives:

    real    0m8.845s
    user    0m6.934s
    sys     0m1.638s
